name: Gramadootha Technical Services
overview: Dialajob, as the name suggests, is a revolutionary phone job-search service dedicated to helping jobseekers find employment and employers find employees fast. This new jobsline is all set to transform job-searching for people looking for work and companies looking to employ. Dialling a single phone number will give the jobseeker information about various job vacancies that suit their profile while employers can get quick results of candidates who go well with their requirement. We intend to serve lakhs of job seekers and thousands of employers, medium and small, who have still not been touched by major portals and newspapers
